com.interpss.core.aclf

Interface AclfLoad

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AcscLoad, DStabLoad, SELoad, Static3PLoad
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfLoadImpl, AcscLoadImpl, DStabLoadImpl, SELoadImpl, Static3PLoadImpl

    public interface AclfLoad
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Load'. ACLF load model class

    The following features are supported:

    • Code
    • Desired Volt Mag
    • DFactor
    • Load CP
    • Load CZ
    • Load CI
    • Parent Bus
    • Dist Gen Power
    • Dist Gen Status
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getAclfLoad()
